description: Fan Sounds for Sleep (10 Hours). Fall asleep fast to the relaxing sounds of fan noise. Fans create natural white noise which is great for drowning out distracting background noises so that you can sleep better at night. This longplaylist can also soothe a crying baby and provide tinnitus relief.
